Detailed Description

cvmx_agl_gmx_rx_prt_info

AGL_GMX_RX_PRT_INFO = state information for the ports

Notes: COMMIT[0], DROP[0] will be reset when MIX0_CTL[RESET] is set to 1. COMMIT[1], DROP[1] will be reset when MIX1_CTL[RESET] is set to 1.
